[src:pydantic-validation/data-validation] It also works well for batch upload, where a file input may be rejected and a set of messages sent back to the input source for why the data is rejected.
[src:pydantic-validation/data-validation] Another form of enforcement action involves automatically changing the data and saving a conformant version instead of the original version.
